Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.91,0:17:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}明日香，初号机这就把刀扔下来，接好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.07,0:17:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}明白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.30,0:17:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}惨了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.11,0:17:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}还没好吗，真嗣
