Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.49,0:19:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}好容易才打赢了，却…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.78,0:19:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}我不要！到此为止了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.45,0:19:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}真嗣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.66,0:19:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}笨蛋，逞什么强嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.00,0:20:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}抱歉打扰了，这里有 NERV 的人在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.56,0:20:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.41,0:20:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}那么请在这里签名
