Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.41,0:20:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}加持先生送来的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.34,0:20:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.84,0:20:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}浴池在那边，左转
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.85,0:20:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}啊，天堂啊天堂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.85,0:20:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}原来洗澡可以这么舒服的，我都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.24,0:20:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}真嗣，听得到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.14,0:20:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}是
