Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.54,0:20:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.14,0:20:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}扔了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.95,0:20:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.67,0:20:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.85,0:20:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}笨蛋，你往哪里扔啊，笨手笨脚的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.12,0:21:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.05,0:21:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}真是的，别打到奇怪的地方嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.68,0:21:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}哪里哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.29,0:21:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}啊！明日香的皮肤胀得红通通的，真好玩喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.92,0:21:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}不要，会痒啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.15,0:21:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}那这里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.45,0:21:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}别碰这种地方啦
